Advanced Features
- Precise Hitscan: Advanced multipoint bone scanning for maximum accuracy with any weapon.
- Visual Intelligence: Highly customizable ESP including box, skeletons, chams, and sound-ESP.
- Zero-Lag Overlay: Built on a custom DirectX 11/12 bridge for minimal frame-rate impact.
- VAC Live Shield: Real-time signature randomization and kernel-level shrouding to bypass Valve's latest security.
- Scripting API: Full support for Lua-based plugins to customize your experience (Skeet-Lua compatible).

